ding-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/trang-diem-co-dau-ngay-cuoi-hoan-hao.html\/#Nhung_yeu_to_de_co_dau_that_hoan_hao_trong_ngay_cuoi\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4 d\u00e2u th\u1eadt ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o trong ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi\">Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4 d\u00e2u th\u1eadt ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o trong ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/trang-diem-co-dau-ngay-cuoi-hoan-hao.html\/#1_Toc_tet_duoc_yeu_thich\" title=\"1. T\u00f3c t\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch\">1. T\u00f3c t\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/trang-diem-co-dau-ngay-cuoi-hoan-hao.html\/#2_Trang_diem_co_dau_tap_trung_vao_doi_mat\" title=\"2. Trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft\">2. Trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/trang-diem-co-dau-ngay-cuoi-hoan-hao.html\/#3_Phong_cach_trang_diem_tu_nhien\" title=\"3. Phong c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean\">3. Phong c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/trang-diem-co-dau-ngay-cuoi-hoan-hao.html\/#4_Chu_trong_trang_diem_nen\" title=\"4. Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng trang \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ec1n\">4. Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng trang \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ec1n<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>V\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi, phong c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m cho c\u00f4 d\u00e2u n\u00ean t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn sang tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 d\u00e2u.<\/p>\n<p>Trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y b\u1ea1n!<\/p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/luu-y-khi-chon-chup-anh-phong-su-cuoi.html\/\">Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ph\u00f3ng s\u1ef1 c\u01b0\u1edbi<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_yeu_to_de_co_dau_that_hoan_hao_trong_ngay_cuoi\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 110%; color: #0000ff;\">Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4 d\u00e2u th\u1eadt ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o trong ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Toc_tet_duoc_yeu_thich\"><\/span><em>1. T\u00f3c t\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch<\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>C\u0169ng theo c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia <strong>trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u \u0111\u1eb9p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi<\/strong> \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1eabu t\u00f3c b\u00edm, t\u00f3c t\u1ebft v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c ph\u1ed3ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, d\u1ecbu d\u00e0ng g\u00e2y thu h\u00fat \u00e1nh nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4 d\u00e2u.<\/p>\n<p>Phong c\u00e1ch b\u00fai t\u00f3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng hay ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c \u0111\u00e1nh x\u00f9 ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 m\u01b0\u1ee3t ki\u1ec3u qu\u00fd b\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, h\u00e3y chia s\u1ebb, trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia trang \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. Ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn cho c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u0103ng hoa v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, trong s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng ng\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1c m\u1eabu t\u00f3c b\u00edm, t\u00f3c t\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c ph\u1ed3ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, d\u1ecbu d\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 thu h\u00fat t\u1eeb \u00e1nh nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4 d\u00e2u khi t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ti\u1ec7c c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2543\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2543\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2543\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/t\u1ebft-t\u00f3c-s\u1ebd-tr\u00f4ng-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-trang-tr\u1ecdng-h\u01a1n.jpg\" alt=\"trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o\" width=\"825\" height=\"464\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/t\u1ebft-t\u00f3c-s\u1ebd-tr\u00f4ng-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-trang-tr\u1ecdng-h\u01a1n.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/t\u1ebft-t\u00f3c-s\u1ebd-tr\u00f4ng-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-trang-tr\u1ecdng-h\u01a1n-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/t\u1ebft-t\u00f3c-s\u1ebd-tr\u00f4ng-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-trang-tr\u1ecdng-h\u01a1n-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/t\u1ebft-t\u00f3c-s\u1ebd-tr\u00f4ng-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-trang-tr\u1ecdng-h\u01a1n-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2543\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ebft t\u00f3c s\u1ebd tr\u00f4ng c\u00f4 d\u00e2u trang tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Trang_diem_co_dau_tap_trung_vao_doi_mat\"><\/span><em>2. Trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft<\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o trang \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ec1n cho khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t, chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn phong c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00f4i m\u1eaft long lanh v\u00e0 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 h\u01a1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat nh\u0169 v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i, vi\u1ec7c l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng qua nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 t\u00ednh nh\u0169 ho\u1eb7c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ph\u1ea3n t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2544\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2544\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2544\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/trang-\u0111i\u1ec3m-m\u1eaft-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-s\u1ebd-l\u00e0m-\u0111i\u1ec3m-nh\u1ea5n-trong-s\u1ef1-ki\u1ec7n.jpg\" alt=\"trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o\" width=\"825\" height=\"464\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/trang-\u0111i\u1ec3m-m\u1eaft-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-s\u1ebd-l\u00e0m-\u0111i\u1ec3m-nh\u1ea5n-trong-s\u1ef1-ki\u1ec7n.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/trang-\u0111i\u1ec3m-m\u1eaft-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-s\u1ebd-l\u00e0m-\u0111i\u1ec3m-nh\u1ea5n-trong-s\u1ef1-ki\u1ec7n-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/trang-\u0111i\u1ec3m-m\u1eaft-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-s\u1ebd-l\u00e0m-\u0111i\u1ec3m-nh\u1ea5n-trong-s\u1ef1-ki\u1ec7n-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/trang-\u0111i\u1ec3m-m\u1eaft-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-s\u1ebd-l\u00e0m-\u0111i\u1ec3m-nh\u1ea5n-trong-s\u1ef1-ki\u1ec7n-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2544\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">trang \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1eaft c\u00f4 d\u00e2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Phong c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c tr\u1ebb trung nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ti\u1ec7c c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chup-anh-phong-su-cuoi.html\/\">Xem th\u00eam d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ph\u00f3ng s\u1ef1 c\u01b0\u1edbi<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Phong_cach_trang_diem_tu_nhien\"><\/span><em>3. Phong c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean<\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1edbi n\u00f3ng \u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho ti\u1ec7c c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi ban ng\u00e0y do v\u1eady, c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ti\u1ec7c c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i.<\/p>\n<p>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o ban ng\u00e0y th\u00ec th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 l\u1ec5 tuy\u00ean h\u00f4n,\u00a0l\u1ec5 \u0103n h\u1ecfi\u00a0v\u1edbi b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng trong kh\u00f4ng gian tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t c\u00f3 m\u00e1t che hay c\u00f3 s\u1ea3nh r\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<p>Theo t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, phong c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, theo phong c\u00e1ch \u00c1 \u0110\u00f4ng,\u00a0trang \u0111i\u1ec3m\u00a0m\u00e0 nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4n l\u00ean v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 d\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/p>\n<p>Phong c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m ki\u1ec3u n\u00e0y mang l\u1ea1i n\u00e9t trong s\u00e1ng, d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec1n th\u1ee5c cho c\u00f4 d\u00e2u.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2545\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2545\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2545\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/trang-\u0111i\u1ec3m-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-t\u1ef1-nhi\u00ean.jpg\" alt=\"trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean\" width=\"825\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/trang-\u0111i\u1ec3m-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-t\u1ef1-nhi\u00ean.jpg 600w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/trang-\u0111i\u1ec3m-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-t\u1ef1-nhi\u00ean-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2545\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Chu_trong_trang_diem_nen\"><\/span><em>4. Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng trang \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ec1n<\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>C\u0169ng theo c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, d\u00f9 ti\u1ec7c c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi ban ng\u00e0y hay chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi trang \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ec1n cho khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng.<\/p>\n<p>Trong th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u00ed h\u1eadu n\u00f3ng b\u1ee9c \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u di chuy\u1ec3n trong su\u1ed1t ti\u1ec7c c\u01b0\u1edbi, c\u00f4 d\u00e2u c\u1ea7n trang \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ec1n th\u1eadt k\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i g\u00e2y tu\u1ed9t m\u00e0u da, ph\u1ea5n n\u1ec1n b\u1ecb ch\u1ea3y l\u00e0m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u m\u1ea5t \u0111i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xinh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i bu\u1ed5i ti\u1ec7c.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2546\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2546\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2546\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/trang-\u0111i\u1ec3m-n\u1ec1n-cho-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u.jpg\" alt=\"trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o\" width=\"825\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/trang-\u0111i\u1ec3m-n\u1ec1n-cho-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u.jpg 680w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/trang-\u0111i\u1ec3m-n\u1ec1n-cho-c\u00f4-d\u00e2u-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2546\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Trang \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ec1n cho c\u00f4 d\u00e2u<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>N\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m cho da uy t\u00edn v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9a ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng d\u1ea7u (oil free) tr\u00e1nh da kh\u00f4 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u00fap gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho da.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam: <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chup-anh-phong-su-cuoi.html\/\"><em>Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u b\u1ea1n d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/em><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>T\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t ch\u00ednh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 khuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng b\u1edfi chuy\u00ean gia trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi, phong c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m cho c\u00f4 d\u00e2u n\u00ean t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn sang tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 d\u00e2u. Trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y b\u1ea1n! Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2547,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[84,63,88,93],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>M\u1eb9o trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u \u0111\u1eb9p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi | \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o s\u1ebd khi\u00ean \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1edf n\u00ean tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n v\u00e0 \u0111ong \u0111\u1ea7y \u00fd ngh\u0129a h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/trang-diem-co-dau-ngay-cuoi-hoan-hao.html\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"vi_VN\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u \u0111\u1eb9p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y c\u01b0\u1edbi\